descriptionHtml:
This is probably the best thing I've ever made with my life tbh. But nonetheless, I give to you, Naomi, my personal and fully customization preset for RaceMenu (only compatible with CBBE of any kind). At first, I got bored just walking around looking at eye candied 4K textures, but then I realized, what am I doing with my life? I thought to myself I can either sit here and look at glorious textures, or I could create something absolutely beautiful. In my case, I did just that.  

Good note - If anyone is willing to make this preset into a follower, I grant, by all means, permission to edit and redistribute for all I ask is credit.

I don't know if this is just me, but whenever I try to download my own file, it doens't show the .jslot and ReadMe.txt. But if anyone can tell me it works for them, that would be great. Just a first mod Jewbie over here.

This isn't just a face model, but more of a whole body model (which the body is a work-in progress, but not fucked up in any way).  This mod uses a lot of different textures to create the final product and which ones you use is your choice completely. I'm just here to recommend mods to get or close as possible to my character without it looking like a screaming banshee with down syndrome (sorry).

If there seems to be any bugs, please let me know and how much you hate it (you won't, you don't have the nose). Also, feel free to send screen shots of your beautified character.

Recommended Settings for Character: I might as well do this before I get asked questions, so I'll go through all the hair styles I think go best with the preset. Keep in mind that I only have the vanilla and KS Hairdo's hairs installed, and not Apachii SkyHair. The slots are: 54, 101, 113, 114, 115, 116, 126,
138, 140, 149, 155, 166, 167, 435. If you recommend any hairs from any other hair mods, please let me know and I'll come up with an update list.

Required Mods (Mostly for compatible scripting, compatible fixing, editing, and actual requirements).

1. CBBEv3 - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
2. RaceMenu - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?
3. SkyUI (Not actually required, but useful in some occasions) Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863/?
4. SKSE (Correct me if I'm wrong, but just in case its required) - Found here: http://skse.silverlock.org/
4.1. SKSE (From Steam, search in the "search the store" and type "SKSE" a lot easier this way)
5. XP32 Maximum Skeleton (Again, not required, but needed for character animations) - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/?

Highly Recommended Mods (Install in this order to get the very similar appearance). (Eyes and hairs install orders don't matter). 

1. No More Ugly Bronze Shine - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29791/?
2. CBBE - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
3. Leyenda Skin - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73512/?
4. Feminine Hands CBBE - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49285/?
5. FemFeet Redesigned - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37022/?
5 1/2. Adorable Face - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61178/? 
6. Leyenda Skin - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73512/?
7. Immersive Saturation Boost - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32064/?
8. KS Hairdo's - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?
8.1. KS hairod's (Use this if you want to use the HDT Physics with the hair) - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?
9. zzjay's wardrobe - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53442/?
9.1. zzjay's wardrobe (Use this if you want to use HDT Physics and Body Sliders) - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/?
10. DYNAVISON - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12525/?
11. Face Light - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13457/?
12. Eyes of Aber - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59192/?
13. The Eyes of Beauty - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
14. Enhanced Lights & FX - Found here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043/?

Note: I do not give permission for my work to be reuploaded, redistributed, or any of that sort anywhere. If this is found in the Steam Workshop, my work has been stolen, or uploaded to anywhere bu this original source.

Q: On a scale from 9 to 11, how dank are your memes?
A: I wish I could count that high.

Q: What race is this preset for?
A: Nord. I do not plan on doing it for other races, but if you have the willpower, you'll do it eventually.

Q: Do you take requests for presets?
A: Yes, I do, actually. I do anywhere from beauty teens to your favorite por***** uh, you know where I'm going with this. (What you do during 12-3).

Q: Was that last question a real question?
A: Yes, I don't have anything else to do with my life, so I might as well create anything given by the beautiful users. Even if it does include, uh, that.

Q: How do we send requests?
A: Send me a picture of the face, because I can't do anything with bodies, and I'll sculpt it. (I swear, if you send me a c*mshot of the person , I'll die, lol).[url=http://textsmili.es/]
[/url]
